{"tid":1633272,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實勇武一直都收緊藍屍皮","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:58:58.000Z","uid":124711,"like":131,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c204fab4663afd2457e068cb23d305ef5079f4ac","tid":1633272,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"小弟返緊奶共港資公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自7月起班廢老藍絲唔係話手足暴力<br />\n<br />\n就係支持警察開槍 日日都聽到出黎行預左比警察打<br />\n<br />\n又話要槍斃曬佢地 總之就極深藍 秒秒係到講<br />\n<br />\n自神獸出現後 班廢老係少左好多出聲 驚自己被人<br />\n<br />\n老豆搵仔被獅鳥 剩係講班人無性 政見唔同就打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住蒙面法果日佢地成日好似食曬春藥咁<br />\n<br />\nHigh撚又跳曬舞 收工係到話搞撚掂你地啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果晚大裝修後 第日星期六開工 個個塊面懞撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似被人質佢地食左幾舊屎咁 又唔敢大聲了<br />\n<br />\n重有唔好唸住藍絲會變 佢地係奶共奶到無邏輯可言<br />\n<br />\n果隻，我日日扮中立撚引佢地出去被手足獅鳥<br />\n<br />\n班垃圾又唔敢，撚佢地捐個藍屍眾籌，又唔肯捐<br />\n<br />\n之後就屌佢地唔夠愛國，更加無聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遍地開花係做得好好，應該繼續做<br />\n<br />\n集中遊行可以示民意，但要思前想後減低損傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化，不割蔗！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，反抗！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n每次都有出前線發夢既手足上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4234bf54c9609ad8ad921142e17256178edd54f","tid":1633272,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6fbe8e6d344eab0118f75c08001985c667bc4b2e","tid":1633272,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:19:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a7b8f9e0cee75b9cf59b076cafd05d91359fc3a4","tid":1633272,"uid":305536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭<br />\n唔係唔出, 遲少少出都得<br />\n如果要出<br />\n裝修黨鐵同建制派, 唔好裝修商店住<br />\n香港一定要有外國人幫手制裁中共<br />\n因為我地唔係只係對住港共, 仲有史上最邪惡既政權<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好以為香港人可以自己解決中共港共</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">如果大家都覺得日日出黎裝修商店, 就可以打贏中共, 我相信全香港人都會出</span></span>"},{"pid":"4b108448771e9061f662ba7faba8313b85d471b5","tid":1633272,"uid":212168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"星期五十八大裝修當日係街見到d廢老個個都頭dupdup又唔敢出聲咁既野  只敢  圍埋細細聲講野同眼光光食花生"},{"pid":"a27e71e707513f8561fd322fb939e54fb24deaf6","tid":1633272,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b108448771e9061f662ba7faba8313b85d471b5","tid":1633272,"uid":212168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"星期五十八大裝修當日係街見到d廢老個個都頭dupdup又唔敢出聲咁既野  只敢  圍埋細細聲講野同眼光光食花生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"好撚心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d285fdaa646643da34fafff411779cef05fd7b62","tid":1633272,"uid":307792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"push 警察唔執法就由我地執法"},{"pid":"9b566b69f44a6315e8834213faecb189a23fc828","tid":1633272,"uid":82068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"一早講左對撚住d藍絲廢老一定要私了<br />\n講道理唔還拖比佢地笑on9咋<br />\n仲會影響埋其他手足"},{"pid":"c973f89f0cfbdb13d9827050874d6afa6ae8f51f","tid":1633272,"uid":32187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c204fab4663afd2457e068cb23d305ef5079f4ac","tid":1633272,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"小弟返緊奶共港資公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自7月起班廢老藍絲唔係話手足暴力<br />\n<br />\n就係支持警察開槍 日日都聽到出黎行預左比警察打<br />\n<br />\n又話要槍斃曬